name: Amor hand printed womens tshirt by Emilythepemily
description:
Amor hand printed womens tshirt by Emilythepemily. 

Originally designed in 2009 for illustrator Emily Boyd's grad cert show at London College of Communication. This moustache design came well before the likes of Urban outfitters and the rest of the world. 

A wonderfully quirky and popular design. Amor meaning 'Love' is a reflection of my love for eccentric British Dandy's and their wonderful facial hair, stubble and moustache's
